Class Move

java.lang.Object
Client.Model.Move
All Implemented Interfaces:
MoveDirections
Direct Known Subclasses:
ComplexMove, StepMove
public abstract class Move extends Object implements MoveDirections
Abstract class representing a move in the game. Implements the MoveDirections interface to provide direction functionality.
